Mix together the chicken, cilantro, VH(R) Sweet Thai Chili Sauce, bread crumbs, egg and VH(R) Soya Sauce until well combined. With wet hands form 8 equal portions onto skewers and form into a sausage-like shape, covering the pointed end of skewer. Roast skewers on a foil lined baking sheet in a 500 degrees F (260 degrees C) oven for 20 minutes or until cooked through. Serve with additional chili sauce for dipping or serve in warmed pita bread garnished with shredded lettuce, diced tomato and slivered onion.